Dialogue: 0,00:00:43.560,00:00:55.640,辉英,,0,0,0,,If we can construct an explicit set of faces, phi 1, phi 2, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,00:00:55.640,00:00:58.640,辉英,,0,0,0,,then we can compute this integration.
