Dialogue: 0,00:01:02.480,00:01:14.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,Right, so let's define a vector b that is equal to integration of a to b phi 1 f dx,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:14.480,00:01:22.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,integration a to b phi 2 f dx, all the way to integration of phi n f dx.
