Dialogue: 0,00:01:27.480,00:01:28.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,we can write the integral for any f.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:28.640,00:01:30.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,So integration of phi 1, phi 2, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:30.480,00:01:32.640,辉英,,0,0,0,,we can also define a matrix A.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:32.640,00:01:43.520,辉英,,0,0,0,,That is the integral of pairwise products of these basis functions.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:43.520,00:01:50.080,辉英,,0,0,0,,Integration of phi 1, phi 1 dx, integration of phi 1, phi 2 dx,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.080,00:01:53.200,辉英,,0,0,0,,integration of phi 1, phi n dx.
